<div id="content"> 
	<span class="graytitle">Changelog for 4.6.1</span> 
	<ul class="pageitem"> 
		<li class="textbox"> 
		<ul> 
			<li>smaller sized images now viewable in all browsers and image editing 
			tools.</li> 
			<li>Fixes to the demo files and User Guide.</li> 
		</ul> 
		</li> 
	</ul> 
	<span class="graytitle">Changelog for 4.6</span> 
	<ul class="pageitem"> 
		<li class="textbox"> 
		<ul> 
			<li>Popup now fully fullscreen compatible.</li> 
			<li>Now the blue store list background loads only when it is needed, 
			not always.</li> 
			<li>Footer font styles now apply to the footer div not only the link 
			in it.</li> 
			<li>Automatic &quot;load 10 more&quot; in list and musiclist views.</li> 
			<li>New wordpress icon.</li> 
			<li>Various bug fixes and enhancements.</li> 
		</ul> 
		</li> 
	</ul> 
	<span class="graytitle">Changelog for 4.5.3</span> 
	<ul class="pageitem"> 
		<li class="textbox"> 
		<ul> 
			<li>Fixes in the User Guide.</li> 
		</ul> 
		</li> 
	</ul> 
	<span class="graytitle">Changelog for 4.5.2</span> 
	<ul class="pageitem"> 
		<li class="textbox"> 
		<ul> 
			<li>Corrected and cleaned up javascript, validated by JSlint.</li> 
		</ul> 
		</li> 
	</ul> 
	<span class="graytitle">Changelog for 4.5.1</span> 
	<ul class="pageitem"> 
		<li class="textbox"> 
		<ul> 
			<li>Smaller images reducing load times.</li> 
			<li>Corrected javascript, validated by JSlint.</li> 
			<li>Included new thumbnails for menu items.</li> 
			<li>Uncompressed javascript and CSS included.</li> 
		</ul> 
		</li> 
	</ul> 
	<span class="graytitle">Changelog for 4.5</span><ul class="pageitem"> 
		<li class="textbox"> 
		<ul> 
			<li>Removed the slide effect causing a white thumbnail while browsing 
			tabs, empty content &amp; empty pages. This improves speed and useability.</li> 
			<li>New navigation Buttons that are more iphone-like and faster to load.</li> 
			<li>New store list image with a music logo.</li> 
			<li>Optimized and fixed a lot of graphics like the thumbnails and the 
			arrow image for speed and efficiency.</li> 
			<li>iPhone style form support.</li> 
			<li>Rounded selection area around the navigation buttons.</li> 
			<li>Fixes to the popup code.</li> 
			<li>Fixed the folder names inside the zip</li> 
			<li>User Guide enhancements.</li> 
		</ul> 
		</li> 
	</ul> 
	<span class="graytitle">Changelog for 4.1</span><ul class="pageitem"> 
		<li class="textbox"> 
		<ul> 
			<li>Fixed User Guide errors and added a new section.</li> 
			<li>Fixed User guide code leading to wrong html code due to false quotation 
			marks.</li> 
			<li>Fixed the confict between the HTTP encoding and the Document encoding.</li> 
			<li>Optimized the popup code.</li> 
			<li>Automaticly go to the bottom of the page when popup gets opened.</li> 
			<li>Fixed package (false links, wrong names, corrupted codes...).</li> 
		</ul> 
		</li> 
	</ul> 
	<span class="graytitle">Changelog for 4.0</span><ul class="pageitem"> 
		<li class="textbox"> 
		<ul> 
			<li>New building structure.</li> 
			<li>navigation buttons are now fully clickable.</li> 
			<li>Faster to load.</li> 
			<li>Smaller and optimized code.</li> 
			<li>bug fixes.</li> 
			<li>enhanced auto-bug repair/avoiding.</li> 
			<li>White text on click on button.</li> 
			<li>Advanced store list.</li> 
			<li>Easier music code list.</li> 
			<li>Mixing of items is now possible.</li> 
			<li>auto-rounding of images in store lists.</li> 
			<li>comments on menu-items.</li> 
			<li>auto-ellipsis on all items with full view in landscape mode.</li> 
			<li>Ability to add lists (ol, ul) in textboxes.</li> 
			<li>added button in top left.</li> 
			<li>popup support.</li> 
			<li>fullscreen support.</li> 
			<li>disable sliding and fullscreen tag.</li> 
			<li>Fewer problems with the sliding.</li> 
			<li>text is &quot;justified&quot; in all paragraphs.</li> 
			<li>added a User-Guide.</li> 
			<li>more Images included.</li> 
			<li>less http request by reducing number of images and scripts.</li> 
			<li>Embedding RSS functionnality.</li> 
			<li>and more...</li> 
		</ul> 
		</li> 
	</ul> 
